  prototype={<>std::optional&lt; uint64&#95;t &gt; AppleAcceleratorTable::Entry::getDIESectionOffset () const</>}>
Returns the Section Offset of the Debug Info <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/appleacceleratortable/entry">Entry</a> associated with this Accelerator <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/appleacceleratortable/entry">Entry</a> or std::nullopt if the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> offset is not recorded in this Accelerator <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/appleacceleratortable/entry">Entry</a>.
